## ask 3: Automation using n8n (Event-Driven Design)

Built an automation workflow using n8n, triggered via webhooks when experiment status updates occur.

Why this matters:

Shows event-driven architecture

Demonstrates automation beyond manual API calls

Reflects real production workflows (notifications, logging, triggers)

