Task 3: Automation using n8n (Webhook-Based Workflow)
## Overview

Task 3 implements event-driven automation using n8n.
An automation workflow is triggered via a Webhook whenever an experiment status update is received.

## Tech Stack

n8n (Workflow Automation)

Webhooks

REST APIs

Postman (Testing)

